{"tid":1229936,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"家明　送比所有奮不顧身的香港年青人","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:12:10.000Z","uid":48390,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47d2c5348ed3a758ef2fd85eda936793a832c1b2","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FPpJTxrGZbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFPpJTxrGZbY&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhso9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=d37fb862\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FPpJTxrGZbY</a><br />\n<br />\n用你4分鐘睇睇段片，提醒自己同身邊所有人 <br />\n香港後生仔係點樣付出 <br />\n去守護全香港 <br />\n<br />\n今日一定要企出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c675aca5513b5b00d22dca77f8b0c1b79de268","tid":1229936,"uid":23651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6ccad02104ea504eb6cd9e86072785ac4cd5b82b","tid":1229936,"uid":157938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，偏頗及不實，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhso9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=f1a56e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a>"},{"pid":"2bd3f0d9f9971286dd44f7736afbe4c59d6df2ea","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc196bc31fd3c46ec7caebd93802d18cc2c26d6","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfc27ec8368dedaf5a5d010760f8d54e74edab8","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de455a170786d4c8bf2457f162f40c4840a4732","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff450ed1b215723abff8dab0da75608f158c1787","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"身心俱疲 但明天繼續<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林奠道你老母臭閪</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c11355703d19e007374df9f9b906466bcccb92a7","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161b5624c3a81bf26907f50c68c0d833acb19ef4","tid":1229936,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"一日就被youtube因版權問題收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}